\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n軟頂唔好慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadff0dd51c83c42c74c639edbcecb376567dff0","tid":231804,"uid":30166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己位定公家位？<br />\n自己位試下搭鐵皮算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算係公家 但個位得我用<br />\n如果泊架軟頂係度係唔係玩完+實漏水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n軟頂唔好慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但聽講硬頂d膠硬化漏水情況更加嚴重<br />\n利申 冇擁有過硬頂"},{"pid":"8b133d114ce72e49be66727854548431266db1ad","tid":231804,"uid":30166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我返工泊車有時都會泊喺樹底，屋企是村屋，又係泊露天，所以買咗兩個半車罩，一個長放放係返工泊車嗰邊，用黎擋雀屎，另一個放在車尾，屋企泊車用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17T66UR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17T66UR.jpg&h=ace418bc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打！"},{"pid":"20601ecd0a8e27e73d6df2367938e66e99f822b7","tid":231804,"uid":47236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:51:08.000Z","msg":"樹底d雀仔痾屎痾到，一日幾灘都夠你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97d1a0403ff086769c4d4628a2f2c4de80ce599","tid":231804,"uid":6171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己位定公家位？<br />\n自己位試下搭鐵皮算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算係公家 但個位得我用<br />\n如果泊架軟頂係度係唔係玩完+實漏水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n軟頂唔好慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但聽講硬頂d膠硬化漏水情況更加嚴重<br />\n利申 冇擁有過硬頂</blockquote><br />\n我自己都係泊公家位晒太陽 有時泊到樹底就好煩<br />\n有d樹液整到一達達 但就咁耐都無漏水問題<br />\n最大問題係無打開蠟 會起鱗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚柒<br />\n利申舊車"},{"pid":"19a3f108f37111b52e17b926fa5b4277851d6ca2","tid":231804,"uid":25179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:39:33.000Z","msg":"包保鮮紙咪得"},{"pid":"b5075f4a02374c1ec0a58a6d94796fbd8bf68772","tid":231804,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我返工泊車有時都會泊喺樹底，屋企是村屋，又係泊露天，所以買咗兩個半車罩，一個長放放係返工泊車嗰邊，用黎擋雀屎，另一個放在車尾，屋企泊車用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17T66UR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17T66UR.jpg&h=ace418bc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打！</blockquote><br />\n其實呢d 咪仲煩, 次次都開收<br />\n收果下又dirty, 又搞埋你件衫<br />\n落雨收仲仆街<br />\n<br />\n我果時用一次dump左"},{"pid":"172ac210d65d7298f68178e6839e6129a27a25f8","tid":231804,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己位定公家位？<br />\n自己位試下搭鐵皮算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算係公家 但個位得我用<br />\n如果泊架軟頂係度係唔係玩完+實漏水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n軟頂唔好慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但聽講硬頂d膠硬化漏水情況更加嚴重<br />\n利申 冇擁有過硬頂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇撚錯"}]}